I’m really sorry.

2
00:00:18.208 --> 00:00:20.500 A:middle L:100% S:80%
- What about?
- My dad.

3
00:00:20.583 --> 00:00:23.167 A:middle L:100% S:80%
- Why?
- He’s so embarrassing.

4
00:00:23.250 --> 00:00:27.125 A:middle L:100% S:80%
“I know a great song called <i>Ruby.</i>
Where’s my guitar?”

5
00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:33.333 A:middle L:100% S:80%
