6
00:00:39.042 --> 00:00:42.167 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Wow. What a nice poster.

7
00:00:42.250 --> 00:00:46.750 A:middle L:100% S:80%
- Do you like auto racing?
- Not really. I just like this race car.

8
00:00:46.833 --> 00:00:48.292 A:middle L:100% S:80%
I like it, too.

9
00:00:49.167 --> 00:00:52.958 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Ah, I know what I like.

10
00:00:56.833 --> 00:01:00.667 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Careful! That chair is ... broken.

11
00:01:00.750 --> 00:01:02.167 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Too late!

12
00:01:05.875 --> 00:01:10.625 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Wow. I like your backyard.
It’s so big.

13
00:01:10.708 --> 00:01:14.375 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Well, it isn’t all our yard.
This part is ours,

14
00:01:14.458 --> 00:01:19.458 A:middle L:100% S:80%
but that part is from the house next door.
Our yard is really small.

15
00:01:19.500 --> 00:01:24.250 A:middle L:100% S:80%
