Can we see it?

16
00:01:24.333 --> 00:01:26.375 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Sure, come on.

17
00:01:29.208 --> 00:01:31.542 A:middle L:100% S:80%
And this is my sister’s room.

18
00:01:34.833 --> 00:01:37.667 A:middle L:100% S:80%
It’s nice. I really like it.

19
00:02:00.375 --> 00:02:03.292 A:middle L:100% S:80%
And this is the game room.

20
00:02:03.375 --> 00:02:05.750 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Table tennis! Cool!

21
00:02:05.833 --> 00:02:07.917 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Yeah, let’s play sometime.

22
00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:10.292 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Sure. We can do that.

23
00:02:20.417 --> 00:02:22.708 A:middle L:100% S:80%
And here’s the living room.

24
00:02:24.417 --> 00:02:27.417 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Wow! That’s a big TV!

25
00:02:27.500 --> 00:02:29.000 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Yeah, it’s great.

26
00:02:29.083 --> 00:02:32.167 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Look at all those DVDs!

27
00:02:37.250 --> 00:02:39.792 A:middle L:100% S:80%
I really like your music.

28
00:02:43.167 --> 00:02:46.917 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Wow! Coldplay. They’re awesome.

29
00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:49.292 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Ed Sheeran! I love his music.

30
00:02:49.375 --> 00:02:52.417 A:middle L:100% S:80%
And there’s Lorde. She’s great.

31
00:02:52.500 --> 00:02:56.875 A:middle L:100% S:80%
And Lil Wayne!
You have rap music, too. Cool!

32
00:02:56.958 --> 00:02:59.333 A:middle L:100% S:80%
This is great music, Tom.

33
00:02:59.417 --> 00:03:03.958 A:middle L:100% S:80%
