You can just download all of this.

34
00:03:04.042 --> 00:03:09.417 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Well, it’s not my music.
It’s my dad’s. He likes to listen to CDs.

35
00:03:09.500 --> 00:03:12.708 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Your dad’s? Really?

36
00:03:12.792 --> 00:03:14.417 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Is your dad a musi...

37
00:03:14.500 --> 00:03:17.000 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Ah, there you are. Good.
Now, sit down, sit down.

38
00:03:17.083 --> 00:03:18.583 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Dad, please.

39
00:03:18.667 --> 00:03:21.333 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Don’t worry. Only one song.

40
00:03:21.417 --> 00:03:25.000 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Sit down, please,
I want you all to listen.

41
00:03:25.083 --> 00:03:26.875 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Dad, please.

42
00:03:26.958 --> 00:03:29.125 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Let’s listen, Tom.

43
00:03:30.667 --> 00:03:33.125 A:middle L:100% S:80%
<i>Ruby, Ruby, Ruby, Ruby,…</i>

44
00:03:35.750 --> 00:03:38.000 A:middle L:100% S:80%
<i>Do you, do you, do you, do you,…</i>

45
00:03:41.208 --> 00:03:43.458 A:middle L:100% S:80%
<i>Know what you’re doing, doing to me?</i>

46
00:03:44.250 --> 00:03:47.000 A:middle L:100% S:80%
- Tom, your dad is really cool.
- Really?

47
00:03:47.125 --> 00:03:49.542 A:middle L:100% S:80%
<i>Ruby, Ruby, Ruby, Ruby!</i>

48
00:03:50.417 --> 00:03:52.375 A:middle L:100% S:80%
Yeah, he is.

